imdb.plot outline: The story revolves around Cody and his new-found alien friend Arbie, who has superhuman abilities due to a device named GIZMO. As our two superheroes avoid the bounty hunter, Pyriss, who is sent by the evil Malzoids. Aside from those threats, they also have to overcome natural threats like volcanic eruptions. Cody will discover more about Arbie's mission: To search for an alien raw material, Macguvitonium which means life and death to Arbie's people. But will their enemies lat their hands on it first or will Cody and Arbie? Will evil triumph over good?

plot: Cody meets an alien, Arbie, and they become fast friends. He helps Arbie in the search for Macguvitonium, vital to Arbie's people. But they're hunted by the bounty hunter Pyriss, sent by the evil Malzoids.

The story revolves around Cody and his new-found alien friend Arbie, who has superhuman abilities due to a device named GIZMO. As our two superheroes avoid the bounty hunter, Pyriss, who is sent by the evil Malzoids. Aside from those threats, they also have to overcome natural threats like volcanic eruptions. Cody will discover more about Arbie's mission: To search for an alien raw material, Macguvitonium which means life and death to Arbie's people. But will their enemies lat their hands on it first or will Cody and Arbie? Will evil triumph over good?
